{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "LocalBusiness",
  "name": "YOUR_BUSINESS_NAME",
  "image": "https://www.yourwebsite.com/business-photo.jpg",
  "priceRange": "$$",
  "telephone": "+1-XXX-XXX-XXXX",
  "email": "info@yourbusiness.com",
  "url": "https://www.yourwebsite.com",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "streetAddress": "123 Main Street",
    "addressLocality": "City Name",
    "addressRegion": "ST",
    "postalCode": "12345",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "geo": {
    "@type": "GeoCoordinates",
    "latitude": 40.7128,
    "longitude": -74.0060
  },
  "openingHoursSpecification": [
    {
      "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
      "dayOfWeek": ["Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday"],
      "opens": "09:00",
      "closes": "17:00"
    },
    {
      "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
      "dayOfWeek": "Saturday",
      "opens": "10:00",
      "closes": "14:00"
    }
  ],
  "sameAs": [
    "https://www.facebook.com/yourbusiness",
    "https://www.instagram.com/yourbusiness",
    "https://www.yelp.com/biz/yourbusiness"
  ],
  "aggregateRating": {
    "@type": "AggregateRating",
    "ratingValue": "4.6",
    "reviewCount": "127",
    "bestRating": "5",
    "worstRating": "1"
  },
  "paymentAccepted": "Cash, Credit Card, Debit Card",
  "currenciesAccepted": "USD",
  "areaServed": {
    "@type": "GeoCircle",
    "geoMidpoint": {
      "@type": "GeoCoordinates",
      "latitude": 40.7128,
      "longitude": -74.0060
    },
    "geoRadius": "50 miles"
  }
}

<!-- 
INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Replace all placeholder values with your actual business information
2. Get accurate coordinates from Google Maps (right-click location > "What's here?")
3. Use 24-hour time format for opening hours (09:00, not 9am)
4. Include all days you're open in openingHoursSpecification
5. Price range: $ (inexpensive), $$ (moderate), $$$ (expensive), $$$$ (very expensive)

REQUIRED FIELDS:
- @context, @type, name, address

RECOMMENDED FIELDS:
- telephone, url, openingHoursSpecification, geo

OPTIONAL BUT VALUABLE:
- image, priceRange, email, sameAs, aggregateRating, paymentAccepted

LOCAL BUSINESS SUBTYPES:
Instead of "LocalBusiness", use more specific types:
- Restaurant
- Store
- Hotel
- Attorney
- Dentist
- HomeAndConstructionBusiness
- ProfessionalService
- HealthAndBeautyBusiness
- LodgingBusiness
- FoodEstablishment
- MedicalOrganization

See full list: https://schema.org/LocalBusiness

OPENING HOURS EXAMPLES:

24/7 Business:
"openingHoursSpecification": {
  "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
  "dayOfWeek": ["Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday", "Sunday"],
  "opens": "00:00",
  "closes": "23:59"
}

Closed on Sundays:
Just don't include Sunday in the dayOfWeek array

Multiple Time Blocks:
{
  "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
  "dayOfWeek": "Saturday",
  "opens": "09:00",
  "closes": "12:00"
},
{
  "@type": "OpeningHoursSpecification",
  "dayOfWeek": "Saturday",
  "opens": "14:00",
  "closes": "18:00"
}

PAYMENT OPTIONS:
Common values: "Cash", "Credit Card", "Debit Card", "Check", "Invoice", "PayPal", "Venmo", "Cryptocurrency"

VOICE SEARCH TIP:
LocalBusiness schema is critical for "near me" searches and voice queries like "find a [business type] near me"
-->
